63}, {\"ngram\": \"vigilance\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it can not just be France and its allies reassuring citizens of the world.\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2850, \"end\": 2856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9767592582734053, \"rank\": 0.023777567880447242, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its allies\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"citizens\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Corporate sponsors and participant nations must update their playbooks to identify, share, disseminate and preempt threats to this event as soon, best, and broadly as possible: Public-private partnerships.\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Corporate sponsors\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"participant nations\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2948}, {\"ngram\": \"their playbooks\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"Public-private partnerships\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. Department of State's Overseas Security Advisory Council has long promoted cooperation with the private-sector security community.\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"State\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"cooperation\", \"from\": 3197, \"to\": 3208}, {\"ngram\": \"the private-sector security community\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since 9/11, the U.S. surged intelligence resources to safeguard U.S. interests at strategic events.\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\