, concerning the responsibility of participant nations, sponsors, and vendors would help spur forewarning of threats.\", \"from\": 5075, \"to\": 5260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5083, \"end\": 5115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympics Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"penalties\", \"from\": 5134, \"to\": 5143}, {\"ngram\": \"the responsibility\", \"from\": 5156, \"to\": 5174}, {\"ngram\": \"participant nations\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5197}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 5199, \"to\": 5207}, {\"ngram\": \"vendors\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5220}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 5252, \"to\": 5259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now is the time for all of us to heed Pierre de Coubertin, a Frenchman himself and the founder of the modern Olympics: \\\"The most important thing in the Olympic Games is not winning but taking part; the essential thing in life is not conquering but fighting well.\\\"\", \"from\": 5262, \"to\": 5525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5300, \"end\": 5319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre de Coubertin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5277}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5291}, {\"ngram\": \"a Frenchman\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5332}, {\"ngram\": \"the founder\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5356}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern Olympics\", \"from\": 5360, \"to\": 5379}, {\"ngram\": \"The most important thing\", \"from\": 53